# KOTO-0180: the koto-audio-tools MML generator emits LF-terminated Rust, and
# its tests (mml.rs) compare that output byte-for-byte against these checked-in
# fixtures. Pin the fixtures to LF so KotoOS's core.autocrlf=true does not
# rewrite them to CRLF on checkout — otherwise
# practical_mml_example_generated_fragment_matches_checked_in_output fails on
# any Windows clone.
examples/** text eol=lf
